title: How did I miss this?
author: VD
content_html: Spacebunny always loved this song. I thought it was funny too, but I never knew a) there was a video, and b) that it was kind of awesome. At first it looks like someone’s home lipsync video, and then you start… recognizing people from the 1990s.
